# Documentation Application

The docs application is a Next.js application used to display information about a web3 project and its technicalities.

## Structure

- [apps/docs/app/](mdc:apps/docs/app) - Next.js App Router pages
- [apps/docs/public/](mdc:apps/docs/public) - Static assets

## Key Features

- Built with Next.js App Router
- Documentation pages organized by feature
- API documentation
